Completed Ralph slice `006Z6-active-member-evidence-atomicity-and-history-closure`.

Key outcomes:

- Active-member results now include complete qualifying service and relaxation evidence in deterministic provenance.
- Reason-only relaxation decisions are rejected.
- Verification locks the member and exact supply/service evidence rows.
- Backdated and same-date decisions are rejected without modifying history; later decisions close prior records without rewriting their snapshots.
- Member Registry and active-status verification share one member-authority evaluator.
- Portal-facing projections remain redacted.
- Sharpened dependent slice `006Z2` with current-record provenance and redaction requirements.

